Charles A. DUN LEAVAY, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. ROCKEFELLER CENTER, INC., et al., Defendants-Appellees. No. 34, Docket 71-1386. United States Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Argued Sept. 16, 1971. Decided Sept. 16, 1971. Charles A. Dun Leavay, pro se. John M. Friedman, New York City, for defendants-appellees.

Before KAUFMAN, ANDERSON and FEINBERG, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM:

The judgment of the court below is affirmed.
